headline: Is It Too Late To Consider DoorDash (DASH) After Its Strong 1 Year Share Price Run?
summary: Wondering if DoorDash at around US$226.72 is still a good entry point, or if the easy gains are behind it? This article breaks down what the current price might imply about value. The stock has had a mixed short term patch, with a 0.6% decline over the last 7 days and a 0.8% gain over 30 days, while longer term returns of 3.2% year to date and 33.4% over 1 year keep interest high.
